{"tid":1917712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"納粹黑警上埋聯合國","createTime":"2020-03-09T15:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T15:53:54.000Z","uid":210995,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"64031d9d126643a7f99d9b155134d6d1ce60375c","tid":1917712,"uid":210995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警務處副處長郭蔭庶出席聯合國人權理事會會議，報告警隊處理反修例事件的情況。<br />\n<br />\n今次是首次有警務處代表在聯合國人權理事會上發言。郭蔭庶表示，警隊經常被指控使用過度武力，是因為大家忽略了，世界上任何警隊都被法律賦予使用合理武力的權力，維持社會秩序和法律，很多時候警方是在別無選擇下，才使用適當武力制止違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">他又指，去年的大規模社會暴亂，令香港的良好治安一夜之間蕩然無存，警隊被指控警暴，是因為一些透過暴力，勒索政府爭取訴求的人，刻意污名化警隊。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605c25a7e99ad11263ab839ded81ea39b6ab0035","tid":1917712,"uid":210995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T15:42:25.000Z","msg":"納粹黑警"},{"pid":"36524355346e8b3917064e793e9cfe37136cee19","tid":1917712,"uid":210995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T15:42:47.000Z","msg":"幾時天有眼 死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f333f7c6935ab955215804debb847e87764b9a7a","tid":1917712,"uid":210995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T15:43:52.000Z","msg":"納粹恐怖分子"},{"pid":"85e4cb9083e1231cb4c4d4ee1f427cdc824fdb53","tid":1917712,"uid":15880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T15:43:53.000Z","msg":"呃下廢老就得啫<br />\n<br />\n去到西方國家我驚你講得唔夠多咋, 納粹香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756512d8453387424d28742ddf73acbd534b32bf","tid":1917712,"uid":210995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc